      <title>美国就业数据引发美联储降息幅度争论，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/latest-gold-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告好坏参半，加剧了有关美联储 9 月份会议上将如何大幅降息的争论，导致金价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/latest-gold-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
