    <item>
      <title>美联储威廉姆斯称现在适合降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-now-appropriate-to-lower-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行行长约翰威廉姆斯表示，鉴于降低通胀和劳动力市场降温的进展，现在央行降低利率是适当的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-now-appropriate-to-lower-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗称美国大选风险暂时抑制金属价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/citi-says-us-election-risk-will-keep-metals-contained-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团表示，11 月美国总统大选的不确定性将抑制全球风险偏好，并可能推迟中国政府的刺激措施，从而阻止金属价格大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/citi-says-us-election-risk-will-keep-metals-contained-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 04:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Petro 解决了哥伦比亚的一场危机，其他危机即将到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/colombia-trucker-strike-is-gustavo-petro-s-biggest-social-crisis-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[古斯塔沃·佩特罗于 2022 年上台，承诺改善数千万哥伦比亚穷人的生活。两年后，受腐败丑闻、内阁不断更替和改革失败的困扰，他本周面临总统任期内最大的社会危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/colombia-trucker-strike-is-gustavo-petro-s-biggest-social-crisis-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:20:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业报告疲软加剧需求担忧，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价下跌，创下四个月来最大单周跌幅，因美国就业报告疲软，加剧了人们对全球最大原油消费国需求疲软的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 23:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布后债券市场动荡，科技股受创：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市受到科技股抛售的冲击，而最新就业报告发布后，债券市场大幅波动，交易员们开始猜测美联储是否会在 9 月份实施超大规模降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 22:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔正在考虑出售 Mobileye 部分股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/intel-is-said-to-explore-sale-of-part-of-stake-in-mobileye</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英特尔公司正在考虑出售其在陷入困境的自动驾驶系统提供商 Mobileye Global Inc. 的股份，这是其重大战略改革的一部分。Mobileye 的股价跌至历史最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/intel-is-said-to-explore-sale-of-part-of-stake-in-mobileye</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
